{"_id":"1c73FPhXZ9Ep47MB","name":"Enchant","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This incantation will enchant any blade, making it magical and thus able to damage beings normally only damaged by such things. The blade will also inflict an additional [[/roll 1d6]] stamina damage in combat. The effect lasts for a [[/roll 1d6]] turns, after which the blade becomes brittle and prone to breakage.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6sWK8szumpsu5XYL","name":"Hammer","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This spell gives the caster enhanced strength, so that their weapons hit like hammer blows. In combat, if the caster hits a target, roll the damage dice twice and take the better result. Lasts for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds of combat.</p>","staminaCost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"B30m5heUABGnRy3l","name":"Foulness","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>When cast this spell creates a stench from beyond the grave so foul that any being, friend or foe, within nearby range loses [[/roll 1d6]] stamina. Only the caster is blissfully resistant to the hideous miasma.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"CiylGArZcLrlh71l","name":"Multiply","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Using magical energies this spell will create [[/roll 1d3]] copies of the caster, which will mirror the actions of the wizard or priest. Enemies will not know which is the real caster. The effect lasts [[/roll 1d6]] rounds.</p>","staminaCost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"CpSXAu2PfKDRjaFA","name":"Alarm","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Casting this spell over an area nearby the caster creates a magical alarm. Anyone entering who is not an ally of the caster sets off the alarm, which is very loud. The alarm lasts one day, or until it is triggered.</p>","staminaCost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"EQbu4dvcTcU9v2W5","name":"Antimagic","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>After casting this spell, the wizard or priest is surrounded by a golden glow. For the next [[/roll 1d6]] rounds, the caster may make a standard incantation test to dispel any magics that target them. If they are successful, the magic is dissipated, if not they suffer its effects as normal.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LlVT6JizZk2Ke83O","name":"Shield","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This spell creates a large shield centred on the caster's arm. It lasts [[/roll 2d6]] rounds, and increases the armour level of the caster, and gives a bonus of 5 to attempts to dodge incoming missile fire.</p>","staminaCost":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"MwoGsqq7195x2mwy","name":"Detection","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This spell allows the caster to detect something within nearby range, so for example in the same room, that is hidden. The caster can ask the games master to reveal a single hidden thing, which they must do. How that information is interpreted is up to the caster.</p>","staminaCost":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"PF8DjYUlDODABaqA","name":"Silence","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This spell creates a bubble of silence that surrounds everyone and everything nearby the caster. The spell lasts [[/roll 1d6]] rounds, during which even the loudest noise cannot be heard (actions inside the bubble make no sound and those outside the bubble hear nothing of what's happening within).</p>","staminaCost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QarnZJlrAbwuHHhu","name":"Speak","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The caster can use this spell to speak to an intelligent creature as if they knew its language. The caster will understand what the being says, and the magic user's words will be automatically translated. Lasts for [[/roll 1d6]] minutes.</p>","staminaCost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"R0eJEABmZuli93IG","name":"Wall","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The caster creates a wall of force between themselves and a target. The wall is six feet high and six feet wide and may be used to block an entranceway. The wall lasts [[/roll 1d6]] minutes, and cannot be penetrated by physical items or beings. It may by penetrated by magical energy.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"RoCV4Y3luj4Dlbxb","name":"Path","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Using this divination spell, the caster is able to determine which of two paths is the safest. There must be two clear options that the caster could take for the spell to be effective, more than this and it will fail. The safer path will be magically pointed out to the caster any anyone else who can see them. Of course, what is the safer path may be open to some interpretation.</p>","staminaCost":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"RoMM2NuCLze2lvZd","name":"Fix","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Stretching and kneading eldritch energies like glue, the caster fixes one being within nearby range to the spot for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds. The target cannot move form that place, although they can sway, move their arms etc. In combat the target can only attack those that come within range and suffers a penalty of 5 to all its attack rolls due to the hindering effect of the spell.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"SD1bUgU18wfasZ8a","name":"Read","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Using magic of the otherworld, the caster can read the surface thoughts of a being within nearby range. Only general impressions can be gained (for example, hostile intent but not exactly what action this will produce). To outside observers except the target, this manifests as a crackling line of energy connecting caster and target.</p>","staminaCost":5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"TPJZ1Rvv3H4kBxug","name":"Unlock","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This spell will unlock any door or padlock, as if the key were used. The lock will glow with an eldritch light for the next three hours, so it will be obvious that it has been tampered with.</p>","staminaCost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"UphdFnO4eFjDxnBT","name":"Blur","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>With a touch, the caster doubles the speed of any one person, such that their movements appear as a blur. This has the specific effect in combat of allowing the target to take two actions in a round (i.e. they can be selected twice to act in a single round), and giving them an additional bonus of 5 to attacks due to the whirling speed of their weapons. The spell lasts [[/roll 1d6]] rounds, after which the target suffers loss of [[/roll 1d6]] stamina due to exhaustion.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"X9cgN0geTAt8BINe","name":"Banish","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Using this spell, the caster is able to send otherworldly creatures back where they came. Once cast, the caster engages in a conflict of incantation skill against any creatures such as demons, angels or undead in nearby range. If successful, the beings are sent back where they came. If unsuccessful, the caster suffers [[/roll 1d3]] additional stamina loss.</p>","staminaCost":5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"XLTBObH5WTuSn6wE","name":"Fear","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Swelling with magical might, the caster projects a sense of fear that is palpable. All enemies in nearby range (i.e. not the caster's allies) suffer a penalty of 3 to all tests due to fear for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds or until the caster is next wounded, whichever comes first.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZiZXaPBzlBfv7SlE","name":"Heal","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This spell allows the caster to heal [[/roll 1d6+3]] stamina either to themselves or to allies. The spell may be cast in combat, but the caster must be touching the target of the spell for it to have effect.</p>","staminaCost":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZjVdk2K6DAkxm6xn","name":"Swarm","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Using an eldritch calling, the caster summons an infestation of vermin most suited to the location (so for example rats in a city). These creatures fill a space nearby the caster, and remain a seething, tumultuous mass for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds, before they dissipate (assuming there's no food).</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZkGEHM0oF73Sedea","name":"Lightning","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This powerful offensive spell sends an arcing lance of eldritch power toward the nearest target within nearby range. The attack automatically hits the nearest person, friend or foe, and inflicts [[/roll 1d6+2]] damage, [[/roll 1d6+4]] if the target is wearing metal armour. The lightning is bright and generates a crack, and is extremely obvious.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZltPjKv1GIhrmJYN","name":"Blast","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This spell generates a ball of fire that rolls in the hand of the caster, and may be flung at a single target within nearby range. It requires a successful ranged attack using the caster's thrown skill against the target's dodge. On a successful hit it inflicts [[/roll 2d6]] damage and may set the target on fire.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZzkrfQMiUZa3ggay","name":"Lock","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Once cast on any lock such as that in a door or a chest, this spell will lock it as if the key had been used. The spell makes a loud popping sound when cast.</p>","staminaCost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"gOxvaanXi79otKrj","name":"Sleep","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This spell drops a target into a deep sleep for [[/roll 1d6]] minutes. The caster must touch the target, which in combat requires a successful brawling attack. When the target awakes it will have no idea what happened.</p>","staminaCost":5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"gRED0H9Br7wbZ5nZ","name":"Servant","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Once cast, this spell summons an ethereal servant to do the caster's bidding. The creature is intelligent, irascible, and critical, but it is able to carry messages and items over vast distances for the caster, travelling at magical speed. The creature remains to criticise the caster for [[/roll 1d6]] hours.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hl2Xpip8bwjoW2Tm","name":"Armour","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The caster creates a suit of shimmering, magical amour about themselves. This counts as heavy armour, and lasts [[/roll 1d6]] rounds. It glows with enough light to act as a dim torch as well.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ie0Eg1EeEK0S1aKX","name":"See","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>With this spell, the caster consults a crystal or other magical gewgaw and can see into the future. What they see is up to the games master, but it should be somewhat pertinent to the situation at hand.</p>","staminaCost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"k5tahJBmQ5YrO0wC","name":"Unseen","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>When cast, this spell renders the caster invisible to enemies in nearby range, although they still make sounds. Allies can still see them, as can enemies who appear after the spell was cast. The spell lasts [[/blindroll 1d6]] minutes, which the games master rolls in secret. While invisible, enemies fighting the caster suffer a penalty of 5 to their rolls.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lcVbyFmcjk4DGGdW","name":"Feather","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The caster slows their fall to that of a feather, escaping harm. The spell lasts until the caster next touches the ground, where the magical energy is grounded with a flash and a smell of ozone.</p>","staminaCost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nOYd8hGocJorVvkJ","name":"Night","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>When this spell is cast, a zone of the blackest night expands around the caster and all those in nearby range. Only the caster and those creatures that can see in pitch black are unaffected. From the outside the spell resembles a cloud of seething darkness.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"oO92fx1Tq8GqC0IG","name":"Fumble","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This spells makes a target clumsy and disorientated. For [[/roll 1d6]] rounds it will be unable to pick up its weapon, make a coordinated attack or do anything else that requires physical coordination.</p>","staminaCost":5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ov63u8jQDOuzH2bL","name":"Float","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The caster gathers magical winds beneath them, and is able to rise ten feet into the air. The spell lasts [[/roll 1d6]] rounds while the caster concentrates, after which the caster drifts back down again. This spell may not be used to arrest a fall, @Item[lcVbyFmcjk4DGGdW]{Feather} is needed for that.</p>","staminaCost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pDgeKn8h6FVDB9gx","name":"Illusion","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>With this spell the caster is able to create an illusion that tricks the eyes of those that see it. The illusion has the maximum dimensions of a table and lasts [[/roll 1d6]] rounds. If the caster stops anything else and concentrates sorely on the spell, they may make the illusion move and produce sound.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pN18EEEgfVjkkPBk","name":"Burn","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The caster is able to manipulate magic to set fire to something within nearby range that is flammable, as if a flaming torch had been held against it for several seconds. This can be used to set clothing alight. During the casting, sparks are visible flying from the caster's hands to the target.</p>","staminaCost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pu9XOzM5RoVRZAl2","name":"Befriend","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This spell allows the caster to change the demeanour of one unfriendly target to one of friendship. It will not affect the target's allies, and the target will act as any other friendly being from that point on (i.e. if the target was attacked, it would become unfriendly once more).</p>","staminaCost":5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"wnEhx5mNRvRcDfwV","name":"Dominate","type":"Spell","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This spell allows the caster to dominate the minds of unintelligent creatures. If successfully cast, the caster has complete control of the creatures mind and may direct it to act as they will, except when this would be obviously damaging to the creature. The spell lasts [[/blindroll 1d6]] rounds, which the games master rolls in secret.</p>","staminaCost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
